- Added `policy_automation_executions` table to record the outcome of each failing-policy automation (webhook, Jira, Zendesk, calendar, conditional access) per host.
- Added `policy_runs` table to track each host's policy transitions: failure count, first time transitioned to failure, and first time recovered.
- Stamped a nullable `policy_run_id` on `host_script_results`, `host_software_installs`, `script_upcoming_activities`, and `software_install_upcoming_activities` so script and software installs triggered by a failing policy can be attributed back to a policy run.
